replies.body:
This is a co-op vs AI problem, you go to play a quick first win of the day, let's take out our frustration blasting some bots and end up in these 30 minute 2v8 slug matches. The MMR range in co-op vs AI is HUGE, like lvl 1-lvl 250. People who have never played ranked in games with Plat players.

That's how you have games like [this
](https://matchhistory.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/#match-details/NA1/3211151205/46270643?tab=overview), I'm trying to teach my 8 year-old how to play and babysit 3 bots at the same time. It was not fun, I was not amused and now my kid thinks that Neeko can always 1 shot people. I'm afraid to play a game with him any time soon.
